    "title": "Immediate Requirement Production Engineer at Reliance Industries",
    "description": "We at Reliance Industries are looking for an experienced Production Engineer based out of Patna. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Reliance Industries:\nReliance Industries is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Industries!",
